    <h3>Why Pneumonia Detection Matters</h3>
    <p>
      Pneumonia is a serious respiratory infection that can become life-threatening if not detected early.
      By analyzing medical indicators, this system assists healthcare professionals in identifying infection
      patterns quickly and accurately.
    </p>

    <h3 class="mt-4">Key Lab Factors Used</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>WBC Count:</strong> Indicates presence of infection.</li>
